('67144a58-abd1-4242-908a-e8590329d15a', '77332d15-72dd-423f-92e6-a2af7167df2b', '1e219e15-676b-4f12-a68a-7914dc965226', 'Faced with this, the individual sizes the decision off a pre-set rule, ignoring the noise and executing the plan mechanically, and true to form extrapolates the last data point into a permanent trend.', 'Lays out the options explicitly, assigns each a rough expected value, and picks the one that survives the numbers — distrusting any impulse that cannot be written down. This time the variable is money moving in real time.', 'Something closer to mild interest than alarm, resolving into relief capitulation — that is essentially forgotten by the next decision.', 0.66, 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
