('d42a159b-f4b4-4230-adea-9a85746c9677', '24822f8d-9fe5-403a-90cb-bde7397221e8', '3ff8c103-531a-428e-be18-bac2aa5c5dd9', 'Faced with this, this profile scales in aggressively, judging the crowd''s fear as the better signal to fade, and true to form assumes the bad statistic applies to other people.', 'Separates the emotional read from the analytical one on purpose, writes both down, and lets the analytical read win the tiebreak. Price action does not care which argument feels more convincing.', 'A momentary tightening before the response settles, resolving into appeasement — that resolves as soon as there is something concrete to act on.', 0.64, 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
