('a6e42551-4863-4c28-bdfe-297a7c7be7f4', '6a5332fb-5190-44d9-b155-bf316bc7d98a', '55b4b68e-8f95-4365-9509-aecebf6cb4b8', 'Faced with this, the individual reacts to the headline before confirming it, then scrambles to justify the trade after, and true to form feels a winning position as fragile and a losing one as merely paused.', 'Keeps every option notionally open as long as possible, even at the cost of the best ones expiring first. The numbers on the screen are the only feedback that matters here.', 'A sharp initial spike of dread, resolving into guilt absorption — that leaves a residue of vigilance well past the event itself.', 0.5, 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('a71b04d5-1a66-42df-8057-04cca629b6ac', '79e03c5f-2a84-4a5b-8eb1-38876792226f', 'cbd05e75-9567-418c-ab4b-2369323703ee', 'Faced with this, this person leans into the move, adding exposure where others are flinching and betting on the reversal, and true to form discounts the older pattern in favor of whatever just happened.', 'Treats the choice as a small research problem: gather the knowable facts first, model the downside, then commit only once the math stops moving. Price action does not care which argument feels more convincing.', 'A momentary tightening before the response settles, resolving into righteous anger — that settles once the choice is made.', 0.66, 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('19918028-01a5-4a11-82c0-fee9812eecf6', '707f8f95-b0c9-4049-a7a9-d76045e3acbd', '0bfee6a1-9c53-4357-956a-97b4a730270c', 'Faced with this, the individual takes the contrarian side deliberately, willing to be early and wrong before being right, and true to form takes the crowd''s confidence as a substitute for its own analysis.', 'Breaks the decision into weighted criteria before looking at gut feel, and lets the tally overrule any single strong reaction. The numbers on the screen are the only feedback that matters here.', 'A flash of heat that cools almost immediately, resolving into righteous anger — that dissolves quickly once the ambiguity clears.', 0.55, 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
