('18f762a8-eb82-4389-8fd8-ca1689af2024', 'f5770d40-edd5-4f2c-b180-7164fd6ecba7', '6733ee11-e30c-4c63-980f-45f0a80d916d', 'Faced with this, this profile acts on the first strong feeling, hitting the button before the reasoning fully forms, and true to form treats being left out of a move as its own kind of loss.', 'Picks the option that resolves the discomfort of choosing fastest, then adapts to whatever follows. This time the variable is money moving in real time.', 'A flash of heat that cools almost immediately, resolving into aggressive counter — that dissolves quickly once the ambiguity clears.', 0.61, 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
('6d47b754-0b7c-49be-b0b5-e715f0344fdb', 'ea370826-c000-45f4-9727-4635c6918cbf', 'be0ed835-4651-4f9c-a1ea-1452ca7f3fea', 'Faced with this, this person de-risks well before the textbook signal, uncomfortable holding exposure into the unknown, and true to form overvalues whatever they already hold simply because it is theirs.', 'Feels most confident the moment someone with more authority confirms the direction, and shaky right up until then. This time the variable is money moving in real time.', 'A quick surge of adrenaline that fades as fast as it came, resolving into appeasement — that dissolves quickly once the ambiguity clears.', 0.65, 'c09637e6-6320-47d7-8d8f-6c374ac2b3fb'),
